childRecords.name: Test Cases/Equipment/CreditCardRegression/TC001_EquipmentSalesAgreement_DiffGateway
childRecords.description:
Objective: Equipment Credit Card Sales Invoicing with different gateways

Steps:
1. 'Book an Equipment Order with Mode of Payment - 'Credit Card'.
2. Add a configuration 
3. Confirm the delivery.
4. Invoice the Order with Credit card

Expected:
Two invoices should get generated in the 'Open Entries' (tfacr2520m000) session - One against Order B.P. and one against Payment Gateway B.P. maintained in the 'Payment Gateway Details' (xiext6100m000) session. Invoice Balance for Invoice against Order B.P. should be $0.
